com.here.sdk.core

Class Location.Builder.FinalBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.sdk.core.Location.Builder.FinalBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    Location.Builder

    public class Location.Builder.FinalBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    After all mandatory fields are set, this builder is returned which allows setting all fields and constructing a new Location instance by calling build.
